long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Enjoy a quick and distraction-free search experience, with SearchThatWebThis is a search-focused extension that offers a default search that is simple and fast.
By clicking “Add to Chrome”, you accept and agree to install the SearchThatWeb extension, set the Chrome™ default search to SearchThatWeb, and to the Terms of Use, and Privacy Policy.

Terms of Use: https://www.searchthatweb.com/terms-of-use
Privacy Policy: https://www.searchthatweb.com/privacy-policy

The SearchThatWeb extension sets your default search provider to Yahoo.

For assistance from our customer service team, please email us at support+searchthatweb@nonline-search.com
